cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.DB, cs.NI, cs.SI 

The paper discusses the use of blockchain for online mapping in smart cities, which involves security and privacy concerns (cs.CR). It also proposes the use of edge computing to improve scalability (cs.DC) and a reputation system to protect against malicious vehicles (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the sharing of data among users and service providers, which falls under the category of networked systems (cs.NI) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
